MinIO(R) exports Prometheus metrics at */minio/prometheus/metrics*. To allow Prometheus collecting your MinIO(R) metrics, modify the *values.yaml* adding the corresponding annotations:

    - podAnnotations: {}
    + podAnnotations:
    +   prometheus.io/scrape: "true"
    +   prometheus.io/path: "/minio/prometheus/metrics"
    +   prometheus.io/port: "9000"

Find more information about MinIO(R) metrics at [MinIO(R) official documentation](https://docs.min.io/docs/how-to-monitor-minio-using-prometheus.html).

